Requirements:
  ids should be unique;
  numberical values only.
  64 bit.
  ordered by date;
  ability to generate over 10,000 unique IDs per second.

For each server: 
64 bit: 
  41 bits: timestamp;
  5 bits: data center id;
  5 bits: machine id;
  12 bits: sequence number;

clock synchronization:
  network time protocol: a time-request exchange with the NTP server.
